<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>emsenn.net</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/sociology/domains/critical-theory/domains/povinelli/domains/settler-colonialism/texts/</link><description>Recent content on emsenn.net</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 30 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://emsenn.net/library/sociology/domains/critical-theory/domains/povinelli/domains/settler-colonialism/texts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Conjecture: The anarchism of the liberal subject derives from civic duty and is thus incommensurable with decolonization</title><link>https://emsenn.net/library/sociology/domains/critical-theory/domains/povinelli/domains/settler-colonialism/texts/liberal-anarchism-is-incommensurate-with-decolonization/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://emsenn.net/library/sociology/domains/critical-theory/domains/povinelli/domains/settler-colonialism/texts/liberal-anarchism-is-incommensurate-with-decolonization/</guid><description>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conjecture :: The &lt;a href="../schools/anarchism/index.md" class="link-internal"&gt;anarchism&lt;/a&gt; of the liberal subject derives from civic duty and is thus incommensurable with &lt;a href="../terms/decolonization.md" class="link-internal"&gt;decolonization&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proof :: unproven&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;claims ::&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Given that liberal &lt;a href="../schools/anarchism/index.md" class="link-internal"&gt;anarchism&lt;/a&gt;, that is, &lt;a href="../schools/anarchism/index.md" class="link-internal"&gt;anarchism&lt;/a&gt; of the liberal subject, requires itself be functional within liberalism and thus a part of liberal worlding, it must maintain compatibility with liberalism.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Given the lineage of liberal &lt;a href="../schools/anarchism/index.md" class="link-internal"&gt;anarchism&lt;/a&gt; is deviation of the lineage of liberal individualism, its a priori determinations may be derived from that lineage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>